OL,5, Tanning salons in Wales are breaking   
OL,6, the law by letting under-18s use their 
OL,7, sunbeds, an undercover BBC             
OL,8, investigation has found.               
OL,10,FSalons in Newport and Cardiff can be   
OL,11,Fseen in footage from BBC Wales' X-Ray  
OL,12,Fprogramme letting in two 17-year-olds  
OL,13,Fwith no ID checks.                     
OL,15,FUnder-18s are banned from using sunbeds
OL,16,Fover concerns they can cause skin      
OL,17,Fcancer.                                
OL,19,FCardiff council said it would review   
OL,20,Ftanning salon practices.               
